Author: Saidles
Text: This is me to a T. Went to the dr recently and got weighed, she told me how much. I know I was wearing doc martens and a heavy brass buckle belt etc but it’s still higher than it was regardless and by god it just threw me off. Combined with the fact I wasn’t feeling great emotionally and it threw off a whole 6 months of doing alright and thrown me back into dumb bitch town. Can’t look in the mirror now without having one of ~those~ moments
